# storage-api core rules

- Go 1.25 service: Supabase Storage-compatible API, direct S3 engines, no PostgreSQL.
- Bucket id `engine:bucket` routes to YAML-configured engines; default engine when omitted.
- English only in code comments and docs; Chinese only in `README.zh-CN.md`.
- Minimal diffs; reuse `registry.Resolve()`, `writeStorageErr()`, existing chi patterns.
- Verify: `go build ./cmd/server && go build ./cmd/preview-worker`.
- See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for commands and architecture.
